"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Antihypertensive response to bendrofluazide in relation to daily dose (in mg, multiply by 10 to get approximate equivalent doses of hydrochlorothiazide). The initial dose of 1.25 mg/day lowers the blood pressure in comparison to placebo; however, higher doses produced little further antihypertensive response. Each treatment group contained approximately 52 patients.",
